quran[63]{c,v,t}:
  76,19,"Bazaba bazengurukwamo n’abana b’abahungu bahoraho (badasaza cyangwa ngo bapfe, babaha amafunguro), ubabonye wagira ngo ni inigi zishashagirana (Lu’ulu’u) zanyanyagijwe"
  76,20,Kandi nunarebayo (mu Ijuru) uzabona ingabire (zitagereranywa) ndetse n’ubwami buhebuje
  76,21,Bazaba bambaye imyambaro y’icyatsi kibitsi ikoze mu ihariri yorohereye n’iremereye. Bazanambikirwamo ibikomo bya Feza kandi Nyagasani wabo azabaha ikinyobwa gisukuye
  76,22,"(Bazanabwirwa bati) \"Mu by’ukuri, ibi ni ibihembo byanyu, kandi umuhate wanyu warakiriwe"
  76,23,"Mu by’ukuri, (yewe Muhamadi) ni twe twaguhishuriye Qur’an mu byiciro"
  76,24,"Bityo, ihanganire itegeko rya Nyagasani wawe, kandi ntuzumvire umunyabyaha cyangwa umuhakanyi muri bo"
  76,25,Kandi ujye wibuka izina rya Nyagasani wawe mu gitondo no ku gicamunsi
  76,26,Na nijoro umwubamire kandi unamusingize igihe kirekire mu ijoro
  76,27,"Mu by’ukuri, abo (bahakanyi) bakunda ubuzima bwo ku isi butaramba, bakirengagiza umunsi uremereye (w’ibihano)"
  76,28,Ni twe twabaremye dukomeza ingingo zabo. Kandi tubishatse twabasimbuza abandi bameze nka bo
  76,29,"Mu by’ukuri, iyi (mirongo ya Qur’an) ni urwibutso, bityo ushaka nayoboke inzira imuganisha kwa Nyagasani we"
  76,30,"Kandi ntacyo mwashaka (ngo mukigereho) keretse Allah abishatse. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Umumenyi uhebuje, Ushishoza"
  76,31,Yinjiza mu mpuhwe ze uwo ashatse. Naho inkozi z’ibibi yaziteguriye ibihano bibabaza
  77,1,Ndahiriye ku (miyaga) yoherezwa ikurikiranye
  77,2,No ku (miyaga) y’inkubi
  77,3,No ku (miyaga) itwara ibicu n’imvura
  77,4,No ku (mirongo ya Qur’an) itandukanya ukuri n’ikinyoma
  77,5,No ku (bamalayika) bazanira amahishurirwa (intumwa za Allah)
  77,6,Kugira ngo bivaneho urwitwazo cyangwa kugira ngo biburire
  77,7,"Mu by’ukuri, ibyo musezeranywa bizasohora"
  77,8,Igihe inyenyeri zizakurwaho (urumuri rwazo rukazima)
  77,9,N’igihe ikirere kizasandazwa
  77,10,N’igihe imisozi izariturwa
  77,11,N’igihe intumwa zizakoranyirizwa hamwe ku gihe cyagenwe (kugira ngo zitange ubuhamya ku bo zatumweho)
  77,12,Ni uwuhe munsi (ibyo byose) byarindirijwe
  77,13,Ni ku munsi w’urubanza (ubwo Allah azakiranura ibiremwa)
  77,14,Ni iki cyakumenyesha umunsi w’urubanza
  77,15,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri babandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,16,Ese ntitworetse abo hambere
  77,17,Nuko tukabakurikiza abo hanyuma
  77,18,Uko ni ko tugenza inkozi z’ibibi
  77,19,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri babandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,20,Ese ntitwabaremye mu mazi asuzuguritse
  77,21,Nuko tukayashyira mu cyicaro gitekanye (nyababyeyi)
  77,22,Kugeza igihe kizwi
  77,23,Nuko tukagena (igihe umwana avukira) kandi ni twe duhebuje mu kugena
  77,24,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri babandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,25,Ese isi ntitwayigize ihuriro
  77,26,Ry’abazima (bayituyeho) n’abapfuye (bayishyinguwemo)
  77,27,"Hanyuma tukanayishyiramo imisozi miremire, ndetse tukabaha n’amazi y’urubogobogo"
  77,28,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri babandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,29,"(Abahakanyi bazabwirwa bati) \"Ngaho nimujye (mu muriro wa Jahanamu) mwajyaga muhinyura"
  77,30,Ngaho nimujye mu gicucu (cy’umwotsi wa Jahanamu) kigabanyijemo amashami atatu
  77,31,Nta bwugamo gitanga ndetse nta n’ubwo kirinda ikibatsi cy’umuriro
  77,32,"Mu by’ukuri, (uwo muriro) utera ibishashi bingana n’inyubako nini"
  77,33,(Ibyo bishashi) bimeze nk’ingamiya z’amagaju
  77,34,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri babandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,35,Uwo uzaba ari umunsi (batazashobora kugira) icyo bavuga
  77,36,Kandi nta n’uburenganzira bazahabwa bwo kugira urwitwazo batanga
  77,37,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri babandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,38,"Uwo uzaba ari umunsi w’urubanza, ubwo (mwe) n’abo hambere tuzaba twabakoranyirije hamwe"
  77,39,"Niba hari amayeri mufite (yo guhunga ibihano byanjye), ngaho nimuyankorere"
  77,40,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri babandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,41,"Mu by’ukuri, abatinya Allah (ku munsi w’imperuka) bazaba bari hagati y’ibicucu (by’ibiti byo mu ijuru) ndetse n’amasoko (atemba)"
  77,42,(Bazaba bafitemo) n’imbuto (z’amoko anyuranye) bazajya bifuza
  77,43,"(Bazabwirwa bati) \"Nimurye, munywe kandi mugubwe neza kubera ibyo mwakoze"
  77,44,"Mu by’ukuri, uko ni ko tugororera abakoze neza"
  77,45,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri babandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,46,"(Yemwe bahakanyi) \"Nimurye munishimishe by’igihe gito (mu buzima bwo ku isi), kuko rwose muri inkozi z’ibibi"
  77,47,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri babandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,48,"N’iyo babwiwe bati \"Nimwuname (musenge)!\" Ntabwo bunama (ngo basenge)"
  77,49,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri babandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,50,Nonese nyuma y’iyi (Qur’an) ni ayahe magambo yandi bazemera